snippet.title: Shattered Heaven - New Trailer
snippet.description:
A betrayal, a dying God, An ancient curse, a divine punishment. 
A forsaken world suspended in time and buried in ashes.
Join the four heroines in breaking the curse and use your skills to win the War of Ascension.

Try the Shattered Heaven demo now and add it to your wishlist on Steam.
